title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
OB: When calling the stored procedure from the Oracle database, the query result is not being displayed in the output parameter of the data set dialog in the query result page.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog of the query result page.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog in the query result page for the presence of the output parameter.
